---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms of Service - CoursesWyn | User Agreement"
  description="Read CoursesWyn's Terms of Service. By using our website, you agree to these terms regarding coupon usage, content accuracy, and disclaimers."
>
  <div class="py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-12">
    <header class="space-y-6 border-b border-slate-700 pb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold bg-blue-500/20 border border-blue-500/40 text-blue-300">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full"></span>
        Legal Document
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-100">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-400">
        Please read these terms carefully before using CoursesWyn.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-100 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-blue-400 rounded-full"></span>
          1. Acceptance of Terms
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            By accessing and using CoursesWyn ("the Site"), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. In addition, when using this Site's particular services, you shall be subject to any posted guidelines or rules applicable to such services.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-100 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-blue-400 rounded-full"></span>
          2. Coupon Accuracy & Availability
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3">
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            CoursesWyn strives to provide accurate and active Udemy coupons. However:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mt-4">
             <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold">•</span>
                <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Coupons have limited redemptions set by instructors (often 1000 uses). We cannot guarantee a coupon will work if this limit is reached before we update the site.</span>
             </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold">•</span>
                <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Prices and discounts are subject to change by Udemy or the instructor at any time without notice.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold">•</span>
                <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">We are not responsible for any purchases made if a coupon code was expired or invalid at checkout. Always verify the price before paying.</span>
             </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-100 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-blue-400 rounded-full"></span>
          3. Amazon & Affiliate Disclaimer
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            CoursesWyn is a participant in the Udemy Affiliate Program. We earn commissions from qualifying purchases made through links on this website. This does not affect our reviews or rankings, which are based on independent analysis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-100 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-blue-400 rounded-full"></span>
          4. Intellectual Property
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            The content, organization, graphics, design, compilation, and other matters related to the Site are protected under applicable copyrights and intellectual property laws. Copying, redistribution, use, or publication by you of any such matters or any part of the Site is strictly prohibited.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

       <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-100 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-blue-400 rounded-full"></span>
          5. Limitation of Liability
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            In no event shall CoursesWyn be liable for any special, incidental, indirect, or consequential damages of any kind, or any damages whatsoever resulting from loss of use, data, or profits, whether or not advised of the possibility of damage, and on any theory of liability, arising out of or in connection with the use or performance of this information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/40 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-slate-100 font-bold mb-3">Contact Us</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-3">
          If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:corrections@courseswyn.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-medium transition-colors">
          corrections@courseswyn.com
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
